name: Wig Installation
description:
This is an add-on service to go along with our custom wigs. The hair will be braided down in a pattern suitable for the type of wig you ordered.

To order this service you have to live in the CHICAGO area and purchased your wig from us. After service is ordered you will be contacted or can contact us on when you would like it done. 

This price includes a braid-down, wig cap if needed, wig installation (sewing around perimeter or just clipping it down), and cutting and styling.

This service can also be ordered directly through contacting us through email at contact.prettygang@gmail.com, using the contact form above, texting 7735400692, or calling 3127180024. This can also be paid in cash in person but still needs to be scheduled using one of the above four ways.

name: Weft Sealing ( Hair that isn't ours!)
description:
Weft sealing helps with hair shedding from being cut or just its natural shedding. ALL OF OUR EXTENSIONS WEFTS ARE SEALED BEFORE BEING SHIPPED! If you send us extensions for a hair service like coloring, clip-ins, etc, you can add on our weft sealing service. 

We don't use products like Fray Check, Dritz, etc. we use products that are specifically made for sealing wefts on hair.

name: Clip-In Extensions
description:
Clip-In Extensions are a good way to change up your hair without the commitment of a sew-in. They are good to add body, length, etc without damage.

This is an add on service. Hair is not included. You can purchase your hair from us or contact us about sending us hair you already have for this service.

Our clip ins are hand made and sold by piece instead of in packs so you have exactly what you want and need. 

MEASURING FOR YOUR PIECES:
1. Part your hair where you want the clip-ins to be placed.
2. Use measuring tape to measure that area and subtract 1-2 inches. This subtraction is to accommodate you being able to wear the clip-ins with versatility without them showing. You can also part off the perimeter of your hair and take the measurements like that.

Depending on the lengths of the clips ordered and the length of hair 1-2 bundles should be enough. All unused hair will be returned to you.

name: Custom Wigs
description:
While ordering your hair, why not get a custom wig to go with it or if you already bought it and would like us to make one, just ship the hair to us!

All custom wigs are constructed with either a spandex dome cap, or netted adjustable cap, depending on preference. Wig combs can be added or the wig can be left without them. These wigs can last a year or longer depending on care.

After order is placed, email us with your name, cap preferred, combs or none, width and length of part opening, and reference picture if needed.

Please allow an extra 1-2 days on processing time for construction.

name: Hair Coloring
description:
Whether it's as simple as dying the hair jet black or as elaborate as a pink, green, and blonde ombre', we can get it done. Our owner is a licensed cosmetologist and she handles all orders personally.

All you have to do is choose the option you would like for your coloring, then you email us with your order number, color thats wanted, and pictures for reference if you need to.

EXPLANATIONS OF COLORING SERVICES:
-Lace Closure Only- the lace closure will only be colored.
-Bundles Only- only the bundles ordered will be colored, whether it's 2,3,4 etc bundles. The price is the same for all bundles. This is for solid colors, regular blonde ombres, etc.
-Lace Closure + Bundles- the lace closure and the bundles ordered will be colored a solid color, blonde ombre, etc.
-Bundles Only Color Ombre- the bundles ordered will be colored with ombre effect with colored dye added. For example, if you want a pink and purple ombre, multi-toned blue ombre, etc.
-Lace Closure + Bundles Color Ombre- the lace closure and bundles ordered will be colored with colored dye added.

Using the contact form above or contact.prettygang@gmail.com to email us.
